HEADWORD: Rumple
<hw>Rum"ple</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fold or plait; a wrinkle.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

